I deleted several &quot;responses&quot; because I wanted to put an end to the 
arguements, but kept canceling. I don&#39;t want to take this &quot;research&quot; 
that serious. 

 I just use the cut and try method for my stuff, there is no 
objective research to it. I am fascinated by the voices, and try 
everything I can to improve reception. I&#39;m not all that concerned 
whether anyone accepts what I do or not. 

 After eight years of doing this stuff, I have no idea how these 
voices are made. Nor do I see any self proclaimed experts out there 
that actually know anything about the paranormal, that makes us all 
about equal. 

 I agree with banning those that insist on arguing, and name calling. 

 Frank-S





